{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_03_01",
  "title": "小美山愛",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインデー前のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、おはようございます！\nレッスンを見に来てくれたんですか？",
      "startTime": 5.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、愛。そういえば、例のバレンタインイベント\nリズノワの出演が保留になってたけど……？",
      "startTime": 12.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すみません……それはまだ決まってなくて……",
      "startTime": 15.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。今いるのは愛だけ？",
      "startTime": 21.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、なんだか落ち着かなくて……\n私だけ早く来ちゃいました",
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "体を動かせば、気もまぎれるかなって",
      "startTime": 30.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……なんだか様子がおかしいな）\n（バレンタインイベントのことで何かあったのか？）",
      "startTime": 37.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "愛、悩みごとがあるなら、相談してみないか？",
      "startTime": 41.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、これは私達LizNoirの問題なので\n{user}さんに頼るのも悪いかなって……",
      "startTime": 49.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ。それに、当事者じゃないからこそ\n言えるアドバイスだってあるかもしれない",
      "startTime": 57.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれません……\nじゃあ、相談に乗ってもらってもいいですか？",
      "startTime": 62.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも……他の人がいる所だと、ちょっと……",
      "startTime": 66.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあレッスンが終わったら俺に連絡してくれ\n事務所のそばの喫茶店で落ち合おう",
      "startTime": 75.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n……{user}さん、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 79.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 83.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 83.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こころが……変？\nちょっとユニークな子だとは思っていたけど……",
      "startTime": 88.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとどころじゃないですよ\nこころはかなり変わった子で……",
      "startTime": 94.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 96.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "――って、何言わせるんですか！　もう！\nそうじゃなくてですね……",
      "startTime": 100.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん。やっと調子が出てきたな",
      "startTime": 102.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 106.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……\n……ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 108.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それでどう変なんだ？　何か心当たりでも？",
      "startTime": 111.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……それがですね\nバレンタインイベントの話が出た頃からなんです",
      "startTime": 119.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 123.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "それ以来、レッスンと食事の時以外は\nずっと部屋にこもってるんです",
      "startTime": 126.9433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインイベントに向けて\n新曲の構想を練ってるみたいなんですけど……",
      "startTime": 131.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 135.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。イベントへの参加の返事を\n保留にしていた理由、もしかしてそれなのか？",
      "startTime": 138.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、お待たせしてすみません……",
      "startTime": 143.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 147.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワがイベントに出るかどうかは\nこころのアイデア次第っていうことになっていて",
      "startTime": 150.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "私も手伝ってはいますけど……\nこころは怖いくらいに必死なんです",
      "startTime": 157.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 161.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 164.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか痛々しいくらいに……\n寝言でうなされてることもあったんです",
      "startTime": 164.9433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 171.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それは確かに心配だな……\nこころに理由は聞いてみた？",
      "startTime": 171.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてみました。そうしたら、自分が目立つために\n頑張ってるだけだ、いつもと同じだって……",
      "startTime": 178.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 182.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、絶対それは嘘だと思うんです\nこころの雰囲気が、普段と違うんです！",
      "startTime": 186.5433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 190.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、寝言言いながら泣いてたんです……\nそんなところ、初めて見ました……",
      "startTime": 194.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "こころは、絶対、何か別の理由であんなに\n自分を追い詰めてると思うんです",
      "startTime": 201.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 204.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_03_01-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "……親友だから\nなんとなく、分かっちゃうんです",
      "startTime": 208.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
